<h1 id="toc1"><span>UncertaintyCrossing</span></h1>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Found&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;dusty&nbsp;corner&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Library</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
