<div class="collapsible-block-content"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/cerastes-informational-file/library"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/cerastes-informational-file/library/medium.jpg" alt="library" class="image" /></a></div>
